{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/parentRule\"><code>parentRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyCSSValue\"><code>getPropertyCSSValue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority\"><code>getPropertyPriority()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyValue\"><code>getPropertyValue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>item()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msGetPropertyEnabled\"><code>msGetPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>removeProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>setProperty()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></strong> 接口表示一个对象，它是一个 CSS 声明块，CSS 属性键值对的集合。它暴露了样式信息和各种与样式相关的方法和属性。</p>\n<p><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> 对象可被暴露于三种不同的 API 下：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/style\"><code>HTMLElement.style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>，用于操作单个元素的样式（<code>&lt;elem style=\"...\"&gt;</code>）。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a> API，举个例子，<code>document.styleSheets[0].cssRules[0].style</code> 会返回文档中第一个样式表中的第一条 CSS 规则。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/getComputedStyle\"><code>Window.getComputedStyle()</code></a>，将 <code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> 对象作为一个<strong>只读</strong>的接口。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.csstext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/cssText\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.cssText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>当前声明块的文本内容。设置此属性会改变样式。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.length\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/length\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.length</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>属性的数量。参照下面的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\" title=\"item()\"><code>item()</code></a> 方法。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.parentrule_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/parentRule\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.parentRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>包含当前声明块的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CssRule</code></a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertypriority\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回可选的优先级，\"important\"。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertyvalue\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyValue\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyValue()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回给定属性的值。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.item\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.item()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      返回用 index 标记的属性名，当 index 越界时返回空字符串。\n      另一个可选方案：使用 nodeList[<em>i</em>]（在 i 越界时返回 undefined）获取。通常在非 JavaScript Dom 实现方案是很有用。\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.removeproperty\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>从 CSS 声明块中删除属性。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.setproperty\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>在 CSS 声明块中修改现有属性或设置新属性。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertycssvalue\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyCSSValue\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyCSSValue()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><strong>仅在火狐浏览器中支持 getComputedStyle.</strong> 返回 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPrimitiveValue\"><code>CSSPrimitiveValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> or <code>null</code> for <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand properties</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"范例","title":"范例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> styleObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssRules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> nameString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nameString<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-cssstyledeclaration-interface","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Reference#索引\">DOM CSS Properties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"范例","id":"范例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration 接口表示一个对象，它是一个 CSS 声明块，CSS 属性键值对的集合。它暴露了样式信息和各种与样式相关的方法和属性。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh